sickle-fibre
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:an unusual wool-fibre in the birthcoat of Romney lambs, similar to halo-hairs.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
